## Standards and standards organizations

The burgeoning, and at times chaotic, landscape of the [Internet of Things](/Internet_of_things) necessitates a concerted effort towards standardization. Without common ground, the promise of seamless interoperability remains an elusive dream. This section outlines key [technical standards](/Technical_standard), many of which are [open standards](/Open_standard), and the influential [standards organizations](/Standards_organization) that are striving to successfully establish them, thereby bringing some semblance of order to the digital wilderness.

